---
const videoUrl = "https://samplelib.com/lib/preview/mp4/sample-5s.mp4";
---

<section class="bg-black min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4 py-16">
  <div class="max-w-7xl w-full">
    <h1 class="text-white text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-center mb-16">
      Characteristics
    </h1>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <!-- Video local -->
      <div class="relative w-full h-96 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
        <video class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg" controls autoplay loop muted>
          <source src={videoUrl} type="video/mp4" />
          Your browser does not support the video tag.
        </video>
      </div>

      <!-- Descripción -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <p class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed">
          SigNa es un intérprete inteligente que traduce señas en tiempo real,
          facilitando la comunicación entre personas Sordas y Oyentes. Su
          tecnología combina Machine Learning y Deep Learning.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Herramientas usadas -->
    <div class="mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-white text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-center">
        Herramientas usadas
      </h2>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
